<div class="content">
    <p><strong style="font-size: 20px; color: black;">Monkey Junior Privacy Policy&nbsp;</strong></p>
    <p>We, Early Start Co. Limited, know that protecting your private information is our priority. This Statement of Privacy applies to the www.monkeyjunior.com and Monkey Junior and governs data collection and usage. For the purposes of this Privacy Policy, unless otherwise noted, all references to Monkey Junior include www.monkeyjunior.com. By using the Monkey Junior App, you consent to the data practices described in this statement.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <strong style="font-size: 20px; color: black;">Collection of your Personal Information</strong><br /> Monkey Junior may collect personally identifiable information such as your name. If you purchase Monkey Junior&rsquo; products and services, we collect billing and credit card information. This information is used to complete the purchase transaction. Monkey Junior may also collect anonymous demographic information, which is not unique to you, such as your age, gender, household income, political affiliation, race and religion. We may gather additional personal or non-personal information in the future.<br /> <br /> Information about your computer hardware and software may be automatically collected by Monkey Junior. This information can include: your IP address, browser type, domain names, access times and referring App addresses. This information is used for the operation of the service, to maintain quality of the service, and to provide general statistics regarding use of the Monkey Junior App.&nbsp;</p>
    <p>Data in our Logs. When you use Monkey Junior or go to a webpage or use an app that has Monkey Junior features (like our &ldquo;Share It&rdquo; button), our system automatically records that information (&ldquo;data in our logs&rdquo;) including information that your internet browser sends whenever you search a App or your mobile application sends when you&rsquo;re using it going to and from different applications. The data in our logs may also include your IP address, the address of the most recent web pages you&rsquo;ve visited that had Monkey Junior features, browser type and settings, the date and time of your request, how you used Monkey Junior, and cookie data.</p>
    <p>Monkey Junior encourages you to review the privacy statements of the Apps you choose to link to from Monkey Junior is not responsible for the privacy statements of other content on Apps outside of the Monkey Junior App.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <strong style="font-size: 20px; color: black;">Use of your Personal Information</strong><br /> Monkey Junior collects and uses your personal information to operate its App(s) and deliver the services you have requested.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> Monkey Junior may also use your personally identifiable information to inform you of other products or services from Monkey Junior and its affiliates, Monkey Junior may also contact you via surveys to conduct research about your opinion of current services or of potential new services that may be offered.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> Monkey Junior does not sell, rent, lease its customer lists to third parties.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> Monkey Junior may share data with trusted partners to help perform statistical analysis, send you email or postal mail, provide customer support, or arrange for deliveries. All such third parties are prohibited from using your personal information except to provide these services Monkey Junior, and they are required to maintain confidentiality of your information.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> Monkey Junior may keep track of the Apps and pages our users visit within Monkey Junior, in order to determine what Monkey Junior services are the most popular. This data is used to deliver customized content and advertising within Monkey Junior to customers whose behavior indicates that they are interested in particular subject area.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> Monkey Junior will disclose your personal information, without notice, only if required to do so by law or in the good faith belief that such action is necessary to: (a) conformed to the edicts of the law or comply with legal process served on Monkey Junior or the App; (b) protect and defend the rights or property of Monkey Junior; and (c) act under exigent circumstances to protect the personal safety of users of Monkey Junior, or the public.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <strong style="font-size: 20px; color: black;">Use of Cookies</strong><br /> The Monkey Junior App may use &ldquo;cookies&rdquo; to help you personalize your online experience. A cookie is a text file that is placed on your hard disk by a web page server. Cookies cannot be used to run programs or to deliver viruses to your computer. Cookies are uniquely assigned to you, and only be read by a web server in the domain that used the cookie to you.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> One of the primary purposes of cookies is to provide a convenience feature to save you time. The purpose of a cookie is to tell the Web server that you have returned to a specific page. For example, if you personalize Monkey Junior pages, or register with Monkey Junior site or services, or cookie helps Monkey Junior to recall your specific information on subsequent visits, this simplifies the process of recording your personal information, such as billing addresses, shipping addresses, and so on. When you return to the same Monkey Junior App, the information you previously provided can be retrieved, so you can easily use the Monkey Junior features that you customized.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> You have the ability to accept or decline cookies. Most Web browsers automatically accept cookies, but you can usually modify your browser setting to decline cookies if you prefer. If you choose to decline cookies, you may not be able to fully experience the interactive features of the Monkey Junior services or Apps you visit.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <strong style="font-size: 20px; color: black;">Children Under Thirteen</strong><br /> Monkey Junior does not knowingly collect personally identifiable information from children under the age of thirteen. If you are under the age of thirteen, you must ask your parent or guardian for permission to use this App.<br /> <br /> <strong style="font-size: 20px; color: black;">Opt-Out &amp; Unsubscribe</strong><br /> We respect your privacy and give you an opportunity to opt-out of receiving announcements of certain information. Users may opt-out of receiving any or all communications from Monkey Junior by contacting us here:&nbsp;<br /> App: &nbsp;www.monkeyjunior.com</p>
    <p><strong style="font-size: 20px; color: black;">Changes to this Statement</strong><br /> Monkey Junior will occasionally update this Statement of Privacy to reflect company and customer feedback. Monkey Junior encourages you to periodically review this Statement to be informed of how Monkey Junior is protecting your information.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> <strong style="font-size: 20px; color: black;">Contact Information</strong><br /> Monkey Junior welcomes your questions or comments regarding this Statement of Privacy. If you believe that Monkey Junior has not adhered to this Statement, please contact Monkey Junior at:&nbsp;<br />Monkey Junior</p>   
    <p>App: &nbsp;www.monkeyjunior.com</p>
